Article by Napi Gazdaság
This year also increased in an average of 16 percent in the trade triangle of Budaörs gold the usual Christmas basket of the Napi newspaper, but in all hypermarkets there was much higher growth than the thousand HUF.
As in December last year, prices in food supermarkets had already been "dispatched", so there was no drastic increase in percentages compared to the high point of departure.
However, it is obviously scary for consumers that what they were able to buy last year at a price well below 9,000 HUF, today they cannot do so even for ten thousand.
